cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a novel road crack detection algorithm based on deep learning and adaptive image segmentation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves training a deep convolutional neural network, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves image processing techniques, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
